nt of time</strong><span> inside. Wooah bro&#8230;negative time&#8230;</spa=
n></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26p=
x; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>This phenomenon arises from quantum mechanics=
, where particles can exist in multiple states at once (</span><em>you guys=
 have watched Dark Matter, right? You get it</em><span>) and exhibit both w=
ave and particle characteristics. When photons pass through atoms, they can=
