m's experiments showed that under certain quantum conditions, this delay ca=
n become negative, making it seem as if the photons leave before they arriv=
e.</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Not going to pretend that this discovery wil=
l have an immediate impact on your life. But, maybe if you&#8217;re bored t=
