e Helene relief efforts. It turns out that comms are super important and ha=
ving a reliable network of satellites connected to an affordable, mobile de=
vice is extremely valuable.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Starlink is going to be on=
