ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Starlink in and of itself is an amazing bu=
siness &#8212; it provides reliable, accessible, and relatively affordable =
connectivity to people throughout the world, often in places that are hard =
to reach. If its mission was simply just to be the best and most important =
satellite internet service provider, it would have loftier goals than 99.9%=
